Privacy Policy for Might & Fury WW2

Effective Date: 05/01/2023

Welcome to Might & Fury WW2. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information. By using our services, you agree to the terms outlined in this policy.

Information We Collect:

We collect email addresses for the purpose of processing orders and facilitating sales.

Purposes of Data Collection:

We use the collected information solely for processing orders and completing sales transactions.

Sharing of Personal Information:

We do not share any personal information with third parties.

Security Measures:

We employ restricted access controls to ensure the security of collected personal information.

Data Retention:

We do not have specific data retention policies in place at this time.

Use of Cookies and Tracking Technologies:

We do not use cookies or other tracking technologies.

User Rights:

Users have the right to request the deletion of their information at any time.

Contact Us:

If you have any questions or concerns about your privacy, please contact us at mightandfuryww2@gmail.com.

Compliance with Data Protection Laws:

As a company based in the USA, we do not fall under the jurisdiction of the GDPR, but we are committed to protecting your privacy in accordance with applicable US data protection laws.
